            "title": "石藥與阿斯利康訂授權協議 將收首付款3,000萬美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">石藥集團(01093)公布，與阿斯利康就開發si RNA藥物訂立合作及授權協議，石藥將收取首付款已達3,000萬美元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：石藥集團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230719_FI_source-web_石藥集團01093-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：石藥集團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230719_FI_source-web_石藥集團01093-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：石藥集團官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司尚有權收取最高5.4億美元的潛在研發里程碑付款，和最高12億美元的潛在銷售里程碑付款，以及基於有關產品年淨銷售額的潛在個位數銷售提成。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">根據協議的條款，石藥與阿斯利康將針對兩個靶點共同發現和開發具有治療腎臟疾病多種適應症潛力的臨床前候選藥物(PCC)。對於每個PCC項目，阿斯利康將有權選擇獲取在全球範圍內或中國以外地區(視乎何者適用而定)開發、生產及商業化的獨家權益。石藥將保留其中一個PCC在中國開發、生產和商業化的權益。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16286954-%e7%9f%b3%e8%97%a5%e8%88%87%e9%98%bf%e6%96%af%e5%88%a9%e5%ba%b7%e8%a8%82%e6%8e%88%e6%ac%8a%e5%8d%94%e8%ad%b0-%e5%b0%87%e6%94%b6%e9%a6%96%e4%bb%98%e6%ac%be3000%e8%90%ac%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241115_FI_source-web_01093.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-07-02 16:41:27",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "全日收市｜港股全日收174點  生科股午後續強  比亞迪小米成恒指支撐",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股全日收升174點，險守23,000關，生科醫藥股午後續強，內險股升，汽車股升幅略收窄，晶片及硬件股全日捱沽。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：石藥集團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241115_FI_source-web_01093.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：石藥集團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241115_FI_source-web_01093.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：石藥集團官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數全日報23,055，升174點或0.76%，今早開報23,071點，升190點或0.83%，全日最高位為上午報23,335，升454點或1.98%，隨即升幅收窄，午後反覆向下，最低見22,953，僅升72點或0.31%。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：石藥集團官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241115_FI_source-web_01093.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：石藥集團官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241115_FI_source-web_01093.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：石藥集團官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"比亞迪。資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/06/img_06aa3434_08.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"比亞迪。資料圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/06/img_06aa3434_08.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">比亞迪。資料圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"Shutterstock圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230719_FI_source_licensed_中國人壽_shutterstock_1200_1.png.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"Shutterstock圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230719_FI_source_licensed_中國人壽_shutterstock_1200_1.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">Shutterstock圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260326_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260326_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中芯國際官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：石藥集團官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241115_FI_source-web_01093.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：石藥集團官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"比亞迪。資料圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/06/img_06aa3434_08.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">比亞迪。資料圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"Shutterstock圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230719_FI_source_licensed_中國人壽_shutterstock_1200_1.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">Shutterstock圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260326_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中芯國際官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數全日跌17點或0.4%，報4,454，今早開報4,528點，升56點或1.25%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生國企指數全日報7,612，升54點或0.72% ; 今早以7,613點開市，升54點或0.73%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">大市成交3,561.18億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月期指升210點或0.92%，報23057，高水2  點 ; 科指期貨跌8點或0.18%，報4, 460，高水6點 ; 國指期貨報7616，升83點或1.1%，高水4點。   </p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">生科醫藥股藍籌股中表現最佳，石藥(01093)升8.32%，報7.55元 ; 信達生物(01801)揚7.22%，報85.35元 ;翰森製藥(03692)升6.42%，報31.52元 ; 中生製藥(01177)升4.76%，報4.62元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"比亞迪。資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/06/img_06aa3434_08.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"比亞迪。資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/06/img_06aa3434_08.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">比亞迪。資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">6月汽車交付量理想，汽車股普遍造好，比亞迪(01211)升8.08%，報78.3元，為表現最佳藍籌股，貢獻恒指32點，6月銷量達40.35萬輛，海外出口創高 ; 小米(01810)也升4.44%，報22.6元，貢獻恒指26點，為恒指兩大支持力量，6月汽交付量超過萬輛。理想汽車(02015)升1.65%，報46.84元 ; 吉利(00175)升2.73%，報17.32元 ;蔚來(09866)逆跌3.05%，報37.56元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內險股升，中國人壽(02628)揚5.33%，報28.08元 ; 中國平安(02318)升2.45%，報52.3元 ; 中國太保(02601)升2.31%，報27.5元 ; 新華保險(01336)升2.36%，報47.38元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"Shutterstock圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230719_FI_source_licensed_中國人壽_shutterstock_1200_1.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"Shutterstock圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230719_FI_source_licensed_中國人壽_shutterstock_1200_1.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">Shutterstock圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">阿里巴巴(09988)升1.78%，報94.5元，貢獻恒指26點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">晶片股隨外圍回落，中芯(00981)全日瀉10.07%，報80.4元，為表現最差藍籌股 ; 華虹宏力(01347)插13.52%，報186.1元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">硬件股跌，聯想(00992)插4.34%，報22.02元 ; 長飛光纖(06869)瀉22.36%，報198.3元 ; 建滔積層板(01888)插15.48%，報83.8元 ; 建滔(00148)跌13.23%，報102.3元 ; 智譜(02513)急挫16.64%，報1,754元 ; 兆易創新(03986)跌18.39%，報969.5元 ;  MINIMAX(00100)瀉11.61%，報368.6元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260326_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯國際官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260326_FI_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中芯國際官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Facebook母公司Meta Platforms計劃出售人工智能(AI)運算能力和模型的使用權，引發市場AI過度投資的憂慮，此外部份AI模型股禁售期滿，引發該類股份沽壓。</p>\n</div>",
